---
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = "Mágico González — Poetry Without Rules";
const description = "A perpetual fugitive, a man out of time. The Salvadoran maestro who played not to win, but because it was beautiful to do so. A meditation on the most irrational and sublime talent in football history.";
const date = "May 2025";
const readTime = "10 min read";
const author = "Francesco B.";

const kindred = [
  { name: "Ronaldinho",     slug: "ronaldinho",    trait: "Spells with a smile",      flag: "🇧🇷" },
  { name: "Garrincha",      slug: "garrincha-manoel", trait: "Dribbling ghosts",      flag: "🇧🇷" },
  { name: "Carlos Valderrama", slug: "valderrama-carlos", trait: "The Wizard",         flag: "🇨🇴" },
  { name: "Riquelme",       slug: "riquelme-juan-roman", trait: "Against the clock",   flag: "🇦🇷" },
];
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>{title} – Legends Database</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description}/>
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://legendsdatabase.com/articles/magico-gonzalez"/>
  <meta property="og:type"         content="article"/>
  <meta property="og:url"          content="https://legendsdatabase.com/articles/magico-gonzalez"/>
  <meta property="og:title"        content={title}/>
  <meta property="og:description"  content={description}/>
  <meta property="og:image"        content="https://legendsdatabase.com/articles/magico-article.jpg"/>
  <meta property="og:image:width"  content="1200"/>
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="630"/>
  <meta property="og:locale"       content="en_US"/>
  <meta name="twitter:card"        content="summary_large_image"/>
  <meta name="twitter:title"       content={title}/>
  <meta name="twitter:description" content={description}/>
  <meta name="twitter:image"       content="https://legendsdatabase.com/articles/magico-article.jpg"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, 'SF Pro Text', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #f2f2f7;
      color: #1d1d1f;
      padding-top: 44px;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero-image-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      height: clamp(320px, 55vw, 580px);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 25%;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0.60);
      transition: transform 8s ease;
    }
    .hero-image-wrap:hover .hero-image { transform: scale(1.03); }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 20%, rgba(0,0,0,0.70) 100%);
    }
    .hero-caption {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 28px;
      left: 40px;
      right: 40px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow-dot { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: #c8a800; }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 52px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: rgba(255,215,0,0.85); }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .hero-meta-sep { opacity: 0.4; }
    .hero-author { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70); font-weight: 500; }

    /* ── LAYOUT ── */
    .article-wrap {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 52px 40px 80px;
    }
    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #6e6e73;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: #c8a800; }

    /* ── PROSE ── */
    .prose p {
      font-size: 16.5px;
      line-height: 1.82;
      color: #3a3a3c;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }
    .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .prose strong { color: #1d1d1f; font-weight: 600; }
    .prose em { font-style: italic; color: #1d1d1f; }
    .prose a {
      color: #c8a800;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,168,0,0.3);
      transition: border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .prose a:hover { border-color: #c8a800; }

    /* ── SECTION HEADING ── */
    .section-heading { margin: 52px 0 18px; }
    .section-heading-accent {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #c8a800;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .section-heading h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      color: #1d1d1f;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    /* ── PULL QUOTE ── */
    .pull-quote {
      margin: 44px 0;
      padding: 30px 36px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border-left: 4px solid #c8a800;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .pull-quote::before {
      content: '"';
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 24px;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 80px;
      color: #c8a800;
      opacity: 0.10;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .pull-quote-text {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 19px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: #1d1d1f;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .pull-quote-attr {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #aeaeb2;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── MARADONA QUOTE — special dark gold ── */
    .maradona-quote {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1400, #2a2000);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 32px;
      margin: 44px 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .maradona-quote::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: -40px;
      top: -40px;
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(200,168,0,0.12);
    }
    .maradona-quote::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -20px;
      bottom: -20px;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(200,168,0,0.07);
    }
    .maradona-label {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c8a800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .maradona-label-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #c8a800;
    }
    .maradona-lines { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .maradona-line {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding-left: 16px;
      border-left: 2px solid rgba(200,168,0,0.35);
    }
    .maradona-attr {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    /* ── STAT STRIP ── */
    .stat-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .stat-box {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px 14px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .stat-val {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      color: #c8a800;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .stat-lbl {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #aeaeb2;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ── PLAYER CARD INLINE ── */
    .player-card-inline {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      border: 1.5px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .player-card-inline:hover {
      border-color: #c8a800;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
    }
    .player-card-inline-badge {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c8a800, #e6c800);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .player-card-inline-body { flex: 1; }
    .player-card-inline-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1d1d1f; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .player-card-inline-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #aeaeb2; }
    .player-card-inline-arrow { font-size: 16px; color: #aeaeb2; transition: color 0.15s, transform 0.15s; }
    .player-card-inline:hover .player-card-inline-arrow { color: #c8a800; transform: translateX(3px); }

    /* ── WRONG PLANET INFOGRAPHIC ── */
    .wrong-planet {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      margin: 40px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .wrong-planet-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #aeaeb2;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .wrong-planet-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .wp-side { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .wp-side.right { align-items: flex-end; }
    .wp-flag { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .wp-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1d1d1f; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .wp-pill {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .wp-pill.gold { background: #fdf8e1; color: #c8a800; }
    .wp-pill.gray { background: #f5f5f7; color: #6e6e73; }
    .wp-divider {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .wp-divider-line { width: 1px; height: 40px; background: #e5e5ea; }
    .wp-divider-icon { font-size: 20px; }

    /* ── KINDRED SPIRITS ── */
    .kindred-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 24px 0 32px;
    }
    .kindred-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      border: 1.5px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .kindred-card:hover { border-color: #c8a800; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .kindred-flag { font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .kindred-body { flex: 1; }
    .kindred-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1d1d1f; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .kindred-trait { font-size: 11px; color: #aeaeb2; font-style: italic; }
    .kindred-arrow { font-size: 13px; color: #d1d1d6; transition: color 0.15s; }
    .kindred-card:hover .kindred-arrow { color: #c8a800; }

    /* ── PHILOSOPHY BOX ── */
    .philosophy-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1400, #2a2000);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      margin: 40px 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .philosophy-box::before {
      content: '✦';
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      left: 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(200,168,0,0.25);
    }
    .philosophy-box::after {
      content: '✦';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 16px;
      right: 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(200,168,0,0.25);
    }
    .philosophy-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c8a800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .philosophy-text {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.5;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    /* ── INTERVIEW BOX ── */
    .interview-box {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      margin: 40px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      border: 1.5px solid #fdf0aa;
      position: relative;
    }
    .interview-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c8a800;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .interview-label-icon { font-size: 14px; }
    .interview-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #3a3a3c;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .interview-attr {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #aeaeb2;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    /* ── EUROPE MAP ── */
    .europe-context {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .ec-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .ec-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .ec-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #1d1d1f; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .ec-body { font-size: 11px; color: #6e6e73; line-height: 1.5; }
    .ec-card.highlight { border-top: 3px solid #c8a800; }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .prose-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e5e5ea, transparent);
      margin: 52px 0;
    }

    /* ── FADE IN ── */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ── MOBILE ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-caption { left: 20px; right: 20px; bottom: 20px; }
      .hero-title { font-size: clamp(20px, 7vw, 34px); }
      .article-wrap { padding: 32px 20px 64px; }
      .prose p { font-size: 15.5px; }
      .pull-quote { padding: 22px 20px; }
      .pull-quote-text { font-size: 17px; }
      .maradona-quote { padding: 22px 20px; }
      .maradona-line { font-size: 15px; }
      .stat-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .wrong-planet-grid { gap: 10px; }
      .wp-pill { font-size: 10px; padding: 4px 8px; }
      .kindred-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .europe-context { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .philosophy-text { font-size: 18px; }
      .section-heading h2 { font-size: 22px; }
      .interview-box { padding: 20px 18px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <Navbar/>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero-image-wrap">
    <img
      src="/articles/magico-article.jpg"
      alt="Mágico González — Poetry Without Rules"
      class="hero-image"
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-caption">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow-dot"></span>
        Player Profile
        <span class="hero-eyebrow-dot"></span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Mágico González<br/><em>Poetry Without Rules</em></h1>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span class="hero-author">{author}</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-sep">·</span>
        <span>{date}</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-sep">·</span>
        <span>{readTime}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ARTICLE -->
  <div class="article-wrap">
    <a href="/articles" class="back-link">← Articles</a>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <div class="prose fade-in">
      <p>Passion for a player or a team is, by definition, irrational. And the corollaries of this irrationality — blind, unwavering faith and sheer adoration — often bring us trouble or embarrassment, as they tend to weaken the consistency of our evaluations.</p>
      <p>In some cases, however, we can overlook logic and surrender to pure passion. So allow me this indulgence: <strong>Salvadoran Jorge Alberto González Barillas</strong> was a marvelous and, above all, infallible player. If I analyze his career through a critic's lens, I see a sky filled with question marks, doubts, and uncertainties. And yet.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/player/magico-gonzalez" class="player-card-inline fade-in">
      <div class="player-card-inline-badge">✦</div>
      <div class="player-card-inline-body">
        <div class="player-card-inline-name">Mágico González</div>
        <div class="player-card-inline-sub">AM · El Salvador · Cádiz CF · 1979–1992</div>
      </div>
      <div class="player-card-inline-arrow">→</div>
    </a>

    <!-- MARADONA QUOTES -->
    <div class="maradona-quote fade-in">
      <div class="maradona-label">
        <span class="maradona-label-dot"></span>
        Diego Armando Maradona
      </div>
      <div class="maradona-lines">
        <div class="maradona-line">"The greatest player of all time."</div>
        <div class="maradona-line">"Technically, he was better than me. I have never seen anything like him."</div>
        <div class="maradona-line">"He was better than me. I come from planet Earth — he comes from another galaxy."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="maradona-attr">Diego Armando Maradona, on Mágico González</div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <div class="stat-strip fade-in">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val">🇸🇻</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">El Salvador</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val">82</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">World Cup Spain</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val">~20</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Goals in best La Liga season</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-val">0</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Major trophies — irrelevant</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-divider fade-in"></div>

    <!-- WRONG PLANET -->
    <div class="section-heading fade-in">
      <div class="section-heading-accent"></div>
      <h2>A Man Out of Time, A Player Out of Place</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="prose fade-in">
      <p>What makes the Central American fantasista feel almost like an exile — a vestige of a world that had already been discarded by football history — is the <strong>pure joy that emanates from every single technical gesture</strong> he performed. A perpetual fugitive, a man out of time, yet eternally unforgettable.</p>
      <p>There is something profoundly anachronistic and Latin American about Mágico's relationship with the ball — a kind of primordial, irrational, and anti-functionalist creativity that seems to belong exclusively to those from that part of the world.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="wrong-planet fade-in">
      <div class="wrong-planet-title">Where He Belonged vs Where He Played</div>
      <div class="wrong-planet-grid">
        <div class="wp-side">
          <div class="wp-flag">✨</div>
          <div class="wp-name">His World</div>
          <span class="wp-pill gold">South American poetry</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gold">Beauty as purpose</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gold">Non-functional creativity</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gold">1961/62 aesthetic</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gold">Anti-functionalist</span>
        </div>
        <div class="wp-divider">
          <div class="wp-divider-line"></div>
          <div class="wp-divider-icon">⚡</div>
          <div class="wp-divider-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="wp-side right">
          <div class="wp-flag">🏟</div>
          <div class="wp-name">His Reality</div>
          <span class="wp-pill gray">1980s European football</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gray">Sacchi's rigid systems</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gray">Cádiz CF, La Liga</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gray">Results above all</span>
          <span class="wp-pill gray">Win or go home</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
    <div class="philosophy-box fade-in">
      <div class="philosophy-label">His Football Philosophy</div>
      <div class="philosophy-text">"Poetry without rules"</div>
    </div>

    <!-- KINDRED SPIRITS -->
    <div class="section-heading fade-in">
      <div class="section-heading-accent"></div>
      <h2>His Kindred Spirits</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="prose fade-in">
      <p>Mágico's football evokes a very specific lineage of players — those who played not to win in the conventional sense, but because <em>it was beautiful to do so</em>. Those for whom the beauty of a move was, in itself, its effectiveness.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="kindred-grid fade-in">
      {kindred.map(p => (
        <a href={'/player/' + p.slug} class="kindred-card">
          <div class="kindred-flag">{p.flag}</div>
          <div class="kindred-body">
            <div class="kindred-name">{p.name}</div>
            <div class="kindred-trait">{p.trait}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="kindred-arrow">→</div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="prose-divider fade-in"></div>

    <!-- CADIZ -->
    <div class="section-heading fade-in">
      <div class="section-heading-accent"></div>
      <h2>Andalusia — The Only Place That Could Embrace Him</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="prose fade-in">
      <p>In Italy, a player like Mágico González would have quickly become a target. I can already imagine him being mocked by the Brera school for his lack of fighting spirit, misunderstood by pragmatists and defensive-minded tacticians. He would have been despised by Sacchi's rigid disciples, who would brand him lazy and shameless in prioritizing beauty over effectiveness.</p>
      <p><strong>With Arrigo Sacchi, a player like him wouldn't have lasted longer than a glass of water.</strong> But luckily, the Salvadoran Magician found refuge in Andalusia — perhaps the only place in Europe that could have truly embraced and celebrated him the way he deserved.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="europe-context fade-in">
      <div class="ec-card">
        <div class="ec-icon">🇮🇹</div>
        <div class="ec-title">Italy</div>
        <div class="ec-body">Sacchi's disciples. Rigid systems. No room for the non-functional. Would not have survived a season.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ec-card highlight">
        <div class="ec-icon">🇪🇸</div>
        <div class="ec-title">Andalusia / Cádiz</div>
        <div class="ec-body">The only refuge. A culture that understood his language. The crowd that made him a God.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ec-card">
        <div class="ec-icon">🇫🇷</div>
        <div class="ec-title">PSG (missed)</div>
        <div class="ec-body">Close to signing. Close to Barcelona too. He chose beauty over ambition — every time.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- INTERVIEW -->
    <div class="interview-box fade-in">
      <div class="interview-label">
        <span class="interview-label-icon">🎙</span>
        Mágico González — Spanish TV, 1980s
      </div>
      <div class="interview-text">"I admit I'm no saint. I love the nightlife, and if you ask me, I'd recommend a little taste of it to everyone — provided you also get something done during the day. I know I'm irresponsible, a terrible professional, and that I'm probably wasting the opportunity of a lifetime. I know all that. But I have a 'locura' in my head: <strong>I don't like to think of football as a job. If I did, I wouldn't be myself anymore. I play only for fun."</strong></div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-divider fade-in"></div>

    <!-- CONCLUSION -->
    <div class="section-heading fade-in">
      <div class="section-heading-accent"></div>
      <h2>The Eternal Gratitude of a City</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="prose fade-in">
      <p>A player like Mágico González shatters all the usual oppositions between idealists and pragmatists, between those who worship beauty and those who worship results. He discards those debates with the arrogance of someone who soars at stratospheric heights — proving that the eternal gratitude of an Andalusian city or a struggling Central American nation can fill the heart <em>far more</em> than a trophy or a place in the history books.</p>
      <p>And if we're being honest, he did achieve results. His Cádiz lived its greatest moments thanks to his unpredictable brilliance. His decisive goals against Mexico propelled El Salvador to the 1982 World Cup. There, despite playing for a weak semi-professional squad, Mágico still earned mentions in some "best XI" selections of the tournament.</p>
      <p>Everything else, as far as I'm concerned, is secondary.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pull-quote fade-in">
      <div class="pull-quote-text">He played simply because it was beautiful to do so. And that, to us, was almost unbearable.</div>
    </div>

    <a href="/player/magico-gonzalez" class="player-card-inline fade-in">
      <div class="player-card-inline-badge">✦</div>
      <div class="player-card-inline-body">
        <div class="player-card-inline-name">Explore Mágico González's full profile</div>
        <div class="player-card-inline-sub">Stats, skills, ratings and career data on Legends Database</div>
      </div>
      <div class="player-card-inline-arrow">→</div>
    </a>

  </div>

  <Footer/>

  <script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.07 });
    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
</body>
</html>